  "text": "## Your Rights  \n**8-Day Response Guarantee**\nWe will respond to your complaint within **8 calendar days** of receipt.  \n**Free Ombudsman Escalation**\nIf you're unhappy with our response, you can escalate to the Financial Ombudsman Service (free and independent).  \n**No Retaliation**\nWe will not penalize you for making a complaint.  \n**Full Investigation**\nWe will thoroughly investigate your complaint and provide a clear explanation.  \n---",
